<h1>COMPANY HISTORY AND MILESTONES OF GROWTH</h1>

<h2>The Health Store has been helping LIVE WELL since 2016</h2>

<p>Our aim is to provide the best selection of alternative medicine, premium vitamins and supplements, health foods, sports nutrition, natural body care and everything else you need for a healthier and happier lifestyle.</p>

                                                              <p>The Company has developed a unique approach to health store retailing and puts considerable investment into recruitment and selection as well as continuous training programs for all staff members. All our product advisors are highly trained and passionate about the ethos of the company and the products we sell.</p>

                                                              <p>There are now 11 stores in the group, 8 in Dublin, 1 in Kildare and 2 in Wicklow.</p>
<p>From the outset there was the drive to provide a premium customer service and to ensure an extensive product range to our customers. The Health Store stocks over 6,000 products, including many of the respected brands in the industry. The Health Store has worked very hard to become one of the leading innovators in the health food sector in Ireland. We have developed a strong reputation for providing the leading product ranges.</p>

                                                              <p> The Health Store are proud to be the exclusive agents for GNC products in Ireland</p>
